  section.section.section-what-is#what-is
    div.section__wrap.container
      h2.section__title What is Boolberry
      p.section__description BBR is a fully secure and anonymous cryptocurrency. Built from the ground up to ensure anonymity, transactions cannot be linked to a single sender.
      div.figure-group
        figure.figure
          div.figure__icon
            img(src=require('./images/fig_blockchain.svg')).figure__img
          figcaption.figure__text
            dl
              dt.figure__strong Solving blockchain bloat
              dd.figure__regular It’s no longer necessary to drag around hundreds of thousands of ring signatures to mantain security. Boolberry's unique pruning mechanism trims old ring signatures that are covered by checkpoints. This results in up to a 90% reduction of block chain size to ensure fast and efficient synchronization.
        
        figure.figure
          div.figure__icon
            img(src=require('./images/fig_defending.svg')).figure__img
          figcaption.figure__text
            dl
              dt.figure__strong Defending against ASICs
              dd.figure__regular Boolberry employs a proprietary algorithm designed specifially to keep real miners in the game. By combating large hardware mining operations, Boolberry remains truly decentralized and safe from a 51% attack.
        
        figure.figure
          div.figure__icon
            img(src=require('./images/fig_wallet.svg')).figure__img
          figcaption.figure__text
            dl
              dt.figure__strong Creating a user friendly experience
              dd.figure__regular Boolberry wallet app will finally bring an easy-to-use experience to Cryptocurrency.  It's unique alias system gives users the option to replace long wallet addresses with a simple alias, such as @yourname.
  // end section-what-is

